<pc>、</pc>集賢校理<pc>，</pc>知<placeName>陵州</placeName>
<pc>，</pc>又知<placeName>洋州</placeName>
<pc>。</pc>
<date notBefore="1078" notAfter="1085">元豐</date>初<pc>，</pc>知湖州<pc>，</pc>明年<pc>，</pc>至<placeName>陳州</placeName>宛丘驛<pc>，</pc>忽留不行<pc>，</pc>沐浴衣冠<pc>，</pc>正坐而卒<pc>。</pc>
</p>
</div>
<div>
<p>崔公度嘗與<name key="文同" type="givenName">同</name>
