<pc>。</pc>嘗注杜甫詩<pc>，</pc>有文集<measure quantity="50" unit="chapters">
<num value="50">五十</num>卷</measure>
<pc>。</pc>
</p>
</div>
<div>
<p>黃伯思<pc>，</pc>字長睿<pc>，</pc>其遠祖自<placeName>光州</placeName>固始徙閩<pc>，</pc>為邵武人<pc>。</pc>祖履<pc>，</pc>資政殿大學士<pc>。</pc>父應求<pc>，</pc>
